### Server Owner Flow
1. Navigate to Dashboard
2. Click "Create Server"
3. Choose plan (check coin balance)
4. Name server & confirm
5. Server auto-deploys (30-60 seconds)
6. Redirected to console
7. Server boots automatically
8. Accept EULA popup (if shown)
9. Server runs - share IP with friends!

### Plugin Installation
1. Go to server console
2. Click "Plugins" tab
3. Filter by Minecraft version
4. Search for plugin
5. Click "Install"
6. Plugin downloads automatically
7. Restart server (one click)
8. Plugin active!

